Should be the deepest place
on the planet.

01:04:44.422 --> 01:04:46.754
There’s of course
an element of fear in it,

01:04:46.841 --> 01:04:51.551
because it’s a risk, and...

01:04:51.596 --> 01:04:56.215
but if you don’t go out and do something in life, nothing happens.

